Act 354 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas As Engrossed: H3/10/25
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 HOUSE BILL 1601
4
5 By: Representatives L. Johnson, McGruder
6 By: Senator J. Dotson
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT REGARDING HIGHER EDUCATION; TO REQUIRE STATE-
10 SUPPORTED INSTITUTIONS OF HIGHER EDUCATION TO PROVIDE
11 CAREER COUNSELING AND OTHER RESOURCES TO CERTAIN
12 STUDENTS; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
13
